    {
      "id": "sybil_11_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_11",
      "description": "Hey there! \ud83d\ude97 I'm parting ways with my absolute pride and joy, and honestly, she\u2019s a total dream! This car has been pampered since day one\u2014it literally looks and smells like it just rolled off the showroom floor. No scratches, no dents, just pure perfection. I've taken such good care of it, and I'm looking for someone who will love it just as much as I have. It\u2019s smooth, shiny, and ready for a new home. Come take a look, you won't be disappointed! \u2728",
      "price": 48500.0,
