    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Presented in absolute showroom condition, this vehicle is the definition of 'mint.' The exterior boasts its original, deep-gloss factory paint, entirely free of stone chips, swirls, or door dings. Every panel gap is laser-straight, and the alloy wheels are pristine with no curb rash. Inside, the cabin remains a time capsule; the premium leather upholstery is supple with no bolster wear, and it retains that distinct new-car aroma. Mechanically, it is flawless, having been exclusively garage-kept and serviced ahead of schedule at certified dealerships\u2014full documentation and a clean history report are included. Every electronic feature and button functions with tactile precision. This is a rare opportunity for a collector or discerning enthusiast to own a vehicle that looks and drives as if it just rolled off the assembly line.",
