    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_9_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_9",
      "description": "Offered is an investment-grade E92 M3 in showroom condition. This specimen features the high-revving, naturally aspirated 4.0L S65 V8, delivering linear power delivery up to its 8,400 RPM redline via eight individual throttle bodies. The M-DCT dual-clutch transmission executes lightning-fast shifts, while the M Variable Differential Lock ensures optimal torque vectoring across the rear axle. The chassis remains taut with impeccable suspension geometry and Electronic Damper Control (EDC) providing adaptive damping characteristics. Every component, from the rod bearings to the throttle actuators, has been meticulously maintained to factory specifications. This is a rare, turn-key opportunity for the discerning collector seeking peak atmospheric performance.",
